# ğŸ¥ Healthcare Management System (Java Servlet & JSP)

A web-based **Healthcare Management System** developed using **Java Servlets, JSP, JDBC, and MySQL**.  
The project focuses on **secure authentication, modular servlet implementation, clean code execution, and UI enhancement**.

