## ğŸ“Œ Project Features

- Secure Login & Logout (Session-based)
- Doctor Management (Add & View)
- Patient Management (Add & View)
- Appointment Handling (Optional extension)
- Clean UI with CSS
- Database integration using JDBC
- Apache Tomcat Server

